    # mc "I know another restaurant that could get involved. The Wurst Delivery, it's a bratwurst place."
    mc "Conosco un altro ristorante che potrebbe essere coinvolto. Il Wurst Delivery, è un posto di bratwurst."

# game/code/scenes/theatre/sm1fs-t005.rpy:277
translate italian sm1fs_t005_c63764c6:

    # vs "Oh, I know that place. Their sausages are really thick and long."
    vs "Oh, conosco quel posto. Le loro salsicce sono davvero spesse e lunghe."

# game/code/scenes/theatre/sm1fs-t005.rpy:280
translate italian sm1fs_t005_295422d0:

    # vs "I always feel so full after ordering from there."
    vs "Mi sento sempre così piena dopo aver ordinato da lì."

# game/code/scenes/theatre/sm1fs-t005.rpy:283
translate italian sm1fs_t005_bc9e8fb5:

    # tl "A pizzeria versus a hotdog place. It's pretty fresh."
    tl "Una pizzeria contro un posto di hot dog. È piuttosto fresco."

# game/code/scenes/theatre/sm1fs-t005.rpy:286
translate italian sm1fs_t005_8ff90dc6:

    # dvh "Hmmm. That could work. Do you think this Wursthaus would be interested in sponsoring the play for a bit of cash, [mcname]?"
    dvh "Hmmm. Potrebbe funzionare. Pensi che questo Wursthaus sarebbe interessato a sponsorizzare lo spettacolo per un po' di soldi, [mcname]?"

# game/code/scenes/theatre/sm1fs-t005.rpy:289
translate italian sm1fs_t005_f4200b3d:

    # mc "I don't know, but I can go find out."
    mc "Non lo so, ma posso andare a scoprirlo."

# game/code/scenes/theatre/sm1fs-t005.rpy:292
translate italian sm1fs_t005_6e5cf213:

    # dvh "Good. Get to it."
    dvh "Bene. Mettiti al lavoro."

# game/code/scenes/theatre/sm1fs-t005.rpy:293
